function Start(idActor, sPowerName, idTarget)

	if bElite then
		Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idSelf, SFX_WARNING_MINOR)
	else
		Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idSelf, SFX_WARNING_MAJOR)
	end
	
	Hydra.Wait(0.2)	
	
	-- Spawn monsters
	for i, spawnerId in pairs(Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "spawners")) do
		Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(spawnerId)
	end
	
	-- Chance to spawn elite
	if bElite then
		for i, spawnerId in pairs(Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "elite")) do
			Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(spawnerId)
		end
	end


	
	local idPlayer = Hydra.ActorGetClosestPlayer(idSelf)
		
end

function Start(idActorSpawned, idActorSpawner)
	-- Freeze the spanw of spawnees to randomize their spawn time

	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idActorSpawned, false)
	Hydra.ActorDisable(idActorSpawned)
	
	Hydra.Wait(Hydra.GetRandomFloat(0, 1.5))

	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idActorSpawned, true)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(idActorSpawned)
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtTargetsFeet(idActorSpawned, idSelf, POWER_SPIDER_FALL)
end
